sequenceDiagram
    actor Member
    actor Manager
    participant Server
    participant Database

    Member->>Server: Register with username and password
    Server->>Database: Store member information
    Server-->>Member: Registration successful
    Member->>Manager: Request to join household (outside of app)
    Manager-->>Member: Provide household code
    Member->>Server: Join household with code
    Server->>Database: Validate household code and add member to household
    Server-->>Member: Join successful